===============
Version 2.11.90
===============

  Features

	+ Embed the session in a GTK+ window with menu and status bars (Mark)
 	+ Move the changes window out of the session (Mark)
	+ No spew of changes at session start with GNOME 2.12 (Mark)

  Fixes 

	+ Allow ignoring changes to specific GConf keys (Mark)
	+ Fix weirdness with window stacking order (Mark)
	+ Fix strings to be more translator friendly (Funda Wang)
	+ Turn lame pygtk deprecation warnings off by default (Mark)
	+ Support shell style globs in ignore lists (Mark)
	+ Don't create ~/.profile_cache unless needed (DV)
	+ Fix issue with sabayon-apply and profile names containing spaces (DV)
	+ Remove stale X lock and socket files to avoid Xnest errors (Mark)
	+ Make closing the save confirm window act like cancel (Mark)
	+ De-sensitize mandatory column when ignore is selected (William Lachance)
	+ Sort the list of users by name (William Lachance)
	+ Ignore changes to our gconf path files (William Lachance)
	+ Fix issue with displaying Firefox changes (John)
	+ Don't allow running Sabayon from with Sabayon (Mark)
	+ Don't allow xscreensaver to lock a proto-session (Mark)
	+ Fix "Clear History" in the details window (Mark)
	+ Prompt for confirmation when closing the details window (Mark)
	+ Fix traceback when making a profile the default (Mark)
	+ Update user associations when a profile is deleted (Mark)
	+ When creating a profile, make sure its name is unique (Mark)
	+ Select another profile on the list when profile is deleted (Mark)
	+ Make the "Base on" combo insensitive if there are no profiles (Mark)
	+ Make all Sabayon windows show a window icon (Mark)
	+ Correctly parse user's full name from GECOS info (Sebastien Bacher)

  Misc

	+ Website updates (DV)
	+ Fix build issue with --prefix and PAM (Mark)

  Translators

	+ Miloslav Trmac (cs)
	+ Kostas Papadimas (el)
	+ Adam Weinberger (en_CA)
